        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2"> Yes, I did neglect to add the 2 that spawn on the far end of the ruins. IMO, they're just not worth the efforts to get them when you've got the rest of the ruins going. Unless I'm grouped there, or with a partner, I generally don't bother with them. Another slight annoyance is that Reavers will attempt to gate if fear breaks when they're low on life. I've never had a problem with any of my targets falling over the side....I have found that if not killed, their fear pathing will take them past the Bubbleheaded guys, and they'll walk down the ramp to the ground below.</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
